SOURCE CODE:
Create the directory:
bin/hadoop dfs -mkdir /mydir2
To list the Hadoop files:
bin/hadoop dfs -ls
To list sub directories:
bin/hadoop dfs -lsr
To view the file:
bin/Hadoop dfs -put/home/grg/datagen_10.txt/data10
To view the file in browser:
Localhost:50070/
Copy the file from local to hdfs:
bin/hadoop dfs -copyFromLocal/home/grg/datagen_10.txt /data10
Copy the file from hdfs to local:
bin/hadoop dfs-copyToLocal /data10 /home/grg/datagen_10.txt
To copy file from the source to the destination
bin/hadoop dfs -cp/data10/datagen_10.txt
To move file:
bin/hadoop dfs -mv/data10
To remove file:
bin/hadoop dfs-rm/data10
